### 13.2 Fuzzy Roll Number Matching

```php
// For unmatched rolls, suggest closest match
// Uses Levenshtein distance

private function suggestMatch(string $rollInExcel, Collection $students)
{
    $suggestions = $students
        ->map(fn($s) => [
            'id' => $s->id,
            'roll' => $s->roll_number,
            'name' => $s->name,
            'distance' => levenshtein($rollInExcel, $s->roll_number)
        ])
        ->filter(fn($s) => $s['distance'] <= 2) // Max 2 character difference
        ->sortBy('distance')
        ->take(3)
        ->values();
    
    return $suggestions;
}
```

